Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our last... summer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next spring, our village will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Such pleasant old memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's been nineteen years since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this hot spring had mixed bathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm damn lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, my glasses have fogged up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ch-ch-cha... Nippon cha-cha-cha-cha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A good chance for a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui-san's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel ashamed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.25,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(40,0)\an8\fs25}Sign: Prohibited
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suspended...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... done...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't win the title, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I glad you're... all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun! Saionji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good to drink sake and enjoy the snowscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Yui isn't back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Saionji-kun is with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't children anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you{not sure who} climb Mt. Kilimanjaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto, I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's because you were outside for all that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean when I was shooting arrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, long before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I did my cold water ablutions at the waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Showering under the waterfall in the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting arrows behind the fire from the torches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were very beautiful.
