Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto, why don't you take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you like to bathe with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you always held your training camp here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Izu...
