Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw... your...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You watched me doing my cold water ablutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay-ba-ck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let me go, Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've returned to your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto, do... I smell of... sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not like what it looked like a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Saionji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. I'll make a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A-kun... is sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die, Saionji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A-kun is sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wake up, Saionji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Saionji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Saionji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Saionji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Saionji-kun. Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun! Saionji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I won't be naughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've learned the shortcut to the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose that's because my behavior is habitually good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On a mountain where there's nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Has there been an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
