Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, young master, it is I, your butler{he's sayiong gramp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it has stopped snowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of picking you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Butler? Could this be Aritomo's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Reception is quite poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the transmitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the location of the snowmobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{not clear what is said }I hope things went well with Ms. Narusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Narusawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he with Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I will pick you up by helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the navigation system,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a charcoal burner's lodge nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A charcoal burner's lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I running?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui's tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,love Yui?
